dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and shading; depths shown by isobaths and soundings. "Triangulation de Pointe-Noire 1950 et 1957 : Levés stéreotopographiques aériens complétés sur le terrain en 1958 : Restitution à l'appareil Poivilliers. Equidistance des courbes : 5 m." Map shows vegetation and forest coverage. Includes index to sheets.
